description.en: Lobby, lift foyer, and amenities tiling across three floors of a Melbourne CBD office tower. Large-format stone-look porcelain, precision-cut thresholds, compliant wet-area waterproofing, and stainless-steel expansion joint trims.
description.zh: 墨尔本CBD写字楼三层大堂、电梯厅及卫生间铺贴。大规格仿石瓷质砖、精准切割门槛、合规湿区防水，以及不锈钢伸缩缝收边条。
